  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://scholarlyontology.aueb.gr/resources/so_instances/so_MLE#Sentence/uw.2083-537X.pam32.2.07/8">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://scholarlyontology.aueb.gr/resources/so_schema/so_MLE#Sentence"/>
    <so:sentence_text>In addition, quantitative methods were applied to assess the number of vessels present in the well (Orton and Hughes 2013: 203-218; Banning 2020: 105-128).</so:sentence_text>
