    <so:sentence_text>The main objective of the project at the initial stage was to gain an essential overview of the site through geophysical surveying and mapping.</so:sentence_text>
    <so:is_part_of rdf:resource="https://scholarlyontology.aueb.gr/resources/so_instances/so_MLE#Article/01.3001.0010.0085"/>
  </rdf:Description>
